</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-173_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">LXPs offer a wide range of interactive and engaging content, including videos, simulations, gamified modules, and social learning features. These elements not only make learning enjoyable but also increase retention and knowledge application.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-175_ pf-heading-1-h3">Microlearning and bite-sized content
</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-177_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">LXPs deliver content in small, digestible chunks, following the principles of microlearning. This approach enables learners to consume information quickly and efficiently, fitting learning into their busy schedules.
