</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-181_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">LXPs facilitate social and collaborative learning experiences, allowing learners to interact with peers, mentors, and instructors. Through features such as discussion forums, chat functionalities, and peer-to-peer feedback mechanisms, learners can share knowledge, exchange ideas, and collaborate on projects.
